<p>My roots are in Haml, Sass, CoffeeScript, and Ruby on Rails; but as time went on, I started favoring the UI side of things and picked up Ember.js.  I now work with either HTML, Sass, and/or Ember on a daily basis. I do dabble occasionally in Swift as well, but not very often these days. And yeah, like everyone else who’s honest with themselves, I also miss CoffeeScript.</p>

